TETRAPOL-KIT with hex file modification

Original repository: http://brmlab.cz/git/tetrapol-kit.git

If you are on MACOS the glib, json-c library is not detected, enter this command before compile:

export LIBRARY_PATH="$LIBRARY_PATH:/opt/homebrew/Cellar/glib/2.80.4/lib"
export LIBRARY_PATH="$LIBRARY_PATH:/opt/homebrew/opt/gettext/lib"

export LIBRARY_PATH="$LIBRARY_PATH:/opt/homebrew/Cellar/json-c/0.17/lib"
